{
  "title": "Sweet Sour Tunisian Prawn Tagine",
  "description": "A sweet and sour Tunisian dish featuring caramelized prawns, this recipe is kid-friendly and flexitarian-friendly, made in an iron-teppan vessel.",
  "cuisine": "Tunisian",
